<pdiv><l ln="419    ">Where suns less ardent cast their golden beams,</l>
<l ln="420    ">And minor Andes pour a waste of streams,</l>
<l ln="421    ">The marsh of Moxoe scoops the world, and fills</l>
<l ln="422    ">(From Bahia's coast to Cochabamba's hills)</l>
<l ln="423    ">A thousand leagues of bog; he strives in vain</l>
<l ln="424    ">Their floods to centre and their lakes retain;</l>
