<pdiv><l ln="209    ">From happier lands I came, the prince returns,</l>
<l ln="210    ">Where no red flaming flood the concave burns,</l>
<pb n="83">
<l ln="211    ">No furious god bestorms our soil and skies</l>
<l ln="212    ">Nor yield our hands the bloody sacrifice;</l>
<l ln="213    ">But life and joy the Power delights to give</l>
