<item>Edward III. crossing the Somme.</item>
<item>Edward III. crowning Ribemond at Calais.</item>
<item>The Six Burgesses of Calais before Edward.</item>
<item>Battle of Cressy, Edward embracing his son.</item>
<item>St. George destroying the Dragon.</item>
<item>Battle of Poictiers, king of France prisoner to the Black Prince.</item>
