<subhead r="smcapit">By <hi r="italic">JOEL BARLOW</hi>, Esq.</subhead></mainhead> <attbytes>25Kb</attbytes><volhead>The Hasty&hyphen;Pudding [1796]</volhead></somhead><reflink></reflink><comcitn><TY>DATA</TY><ID>Z200140167</ID><A1>Barlow, Joel, 1754-1812</A1><T1>THE HASTY&hyphen;PUDDING: A POEM, IN THREE CANTOS.  WRITTEN AT CHAMBERY, IN SAVOY, JAN. 1793.  By JOEL BARLOW, Esq.</T1><PBL>Published by Joseph Milligan</PBL><Y1>1825</Y1><T2>An Elegy [1782]</T2><T3>Literature Online</T3></comcitn></comhd2>
